  "question_id": "65e07cf2-c23e-4c30-bf23-d6fb31f714d3",
  "short_text": "Hollow Right Angled Triangle - 5",
  "content": "Given a number `N`, write a program to print the **Hollow Right Angled Triangle** of `N` rows using stars (`*`).\r\n\r\n```\r\n      *\r\n    * *\r\n  *   *\r\n* * * *\r\n```\r\n\r\n<MultiLineNote>\r\nThere is a space after every star (`*`).\r\n</MultiLineNote>\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n####Input\r\n\r\nThe input will be a single line containing an integer representing `N`.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n####Output\r\n\r\nThe output should be `N` rows containing stars (`*`) as the **Hollow Right Angled Triangle** shown in the sample output.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n#### Explanation\r\n\r\nFor example, if the given number is `N = 5`,\r\n\r\n- Print the stars (`*`) on **5** rows as shown in the given image.\r\n\r\n<Img imageSrc='https://assets.ccbp.in/frontend/content/programming-foundations/cx-hollow-right-angled-triangle-5.png' widthPercent='70'/>\r\n\r\n<MultiLineNote>\r\n\r\nIn the given image,\r\n\r\n- The Empty box indicates two spaces (\"&nbsp;&nbsp;\").\r\n- The Star in the box indicates the star and a space (\"\\* \").\r\n\r\n</MultiLineNote>\r\n\r\nThe output should be,\r\n\r\n```\r\n        *\r\n      * *\r\n    *   *\r\n  *     *\r\n* * * * *\r\n\r\n```",
  "question_type": "CODING",
  "content_type": "MARKDOWN",
  "codes": [
    {
      "code_id": "67ebb69c-f6a0-4444-bab2-a904a4382190",
      "code_content": "n = int(input())\n\nleft_spaces = \" \" * 2 * (n - 1)\nfirst_row = left_spaces + \"*\"\nprint(first_row)\n\nfor i in range(1, n - 1):\n    left_spaces = \" \" * 2 * (n - i - 1)\n    middle_spaces = \" \" * (2 * (i) - 1)\n    row = left_spaces + \"*\" + middle_spaces + \"*\"\n    print(row)\n    \nlast_row = \"* \" * n\nprint(last_row)",
      "language": "PYTHON",
      "default_code": true
    }
  ],
